rows.label: bf06240100_0010
rows.name: We have been expecting you, Your Highness.

rows.label: bf06240100_0020
rows.name:
Yeah, yeah. Good to see ya.
Is the old man inside?

rows.label: bf06240100_0030
rows.name: Indeed. He has been eagerly awaiting your return.

rows.label: bf06240100_0040
rows.name: Hah! Now I know you're lying.

rows.label: bf06240100_0050
rows.name:
Armus'll fly before that
man welcomes me home.

rows.label: bf06240100_0060
rows.name: No need to coddle me, mate.

rows.label: bf06240100_0080
rows.name:
Any case, seems he knows we're coming.
That'll save time.

rows.label: bf06240100_0145
rows.name:
It true Hana able to produce own
reserves of ether energy, but...

rows.label: bf06240100_0150
rows.name:
I'll explain later.
For now, just do as I ask.

rows.label: bf06240100_0160
rows.name:
All right then.
Leave it to Tora.
